	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I find the extended features of the VRC6 a bit confusing at times, and no game ever used them.  Accordingly, I've created a test rom to help implement the chip correctly.  But since the test rom was created from my own understanding of the chip, it may be wrong.<br /><br />If it wouldn't be too much trouble, I would appreciate it if someone could run this test rom on real hardware.  both iNES 24 and 26 variants are included; running either would be sufficient.<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.mediafire.com/download/6hvuj53omv8y3fn/vrc6test.zip">http://www.mediafire.com/download/6hvuj ... c6test.zip</a><!-- m --><br /><br />The test is fully automatic, and after approximately 8 seconds or less, will print a message on the screen.<br /><br />Thank you!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


