		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I am also interested to see it tested with actual VRC6 cartridges. We can figure out more how it works, and therefore to fix emulators and so on to support these features. Although no existing games use it, it is necessary to make a complete VRC6 implementation, and may be useful in future in case someone is writing more programs that use VRC6 mapper.

		

