	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I don't know if it's still useful anymore, but I came across this post shortly after I finished putting sockets on an Esper Dreams 2 cart to try out the translation, so I thought I'd give your test a try.  I used vrc26test mirrored to fill 28f512s, and when I ran it in my top loader with famicom adapter, I got &quot;All Tests Passed!&quot;  Also, the translation worked!<br />Oh, just in case, the chip is a<br />053329<br />VRC VI  1105-0039<br />9010EAY

		

		</td>
	</tr>
